","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫「你」「我」比較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作文唔係你就我架啦，唔通格硬用「他」咩</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明有咩特別，自己講下自己點解要死，唔用我，點講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1d1a86d2533c45c9536c8b1059edd2e9a12e93","tid":479180,"uid":33907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩叫「你」「我」比較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作文唔係你就我架啦，唔通格硬用「他」咩</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明有咩特別，自己講下自己點解要死，唔用我，點講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n在下，鄙人，吾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193cfc1a96d8fd0de63dfd4580ebb1105a1be7e2","tid":479180,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社會對男性要求太高，支援太少</blockquote><br />\n連登班女權撚唔係咁認為，佢哋成日覺得自己好撚慘"},{"pid":"d42b5667bea9335c0633ec9db8dca1e36fe280e3","tid":479180,"uid":33848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"你對不起我"},{"pid":"a7208482b05b3b679c4a34ca7dfff1cb743b5874","tid":479180,"uid":145769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你對不起我</blockquote><br />\n你有歉疚"},{"pid":"eb2de641076245bb4054945d4eeaf2056a9040f1","tid":479180,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:18:33.000Z","msg":"呢d 鳩會 攞香港錢養垃圾。"},{"pid":"7bc4597ec0664a310db5cc743d7bd514c36b3181","tid":479180,"uid":65005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"不如睇下蔡若蓮個仔自殺個陣有冇寫遺書，如果有，不如拎出黎研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁得閒研究人地封遺書 都唔好好諗下點樣降低青年自殺率"},{"pid":"27d387e3d1cc20d984e8e1ccc91d62374de20dc2","tid":479180,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:39:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">反映自殺者重視與人關係，亦因自己行為感到歉疚，但遺書接收人、例如父母，往往會說「你唔需要道歉」，反倒責備自己做得不足，未了解子女需要。</span><br />\n<br />\n即係唔係父母問題,唔係向父母報仇,咁即係學校同社會出事。"},{"pid":"261eb570e20990e0ed51348dd079dd05ecb83aaa","tid":479180,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"呃funding嘅研究<br />\n加呃稿費嘅01"},{"pid":"76c32140b4c5daac1724dcf68887cd934ce34957","tid":479180,"uid":25758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"（設計遺書）<br />\n<br />\n你個死八婆，我屌你老母，成日迫我講對不起，依家我就死比你睇，你食屎啦，我做鬼都唔放過你"}]}